This paper deals with generating adversarial examples for images, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) category. The paper also leverages generative models, which is a common technique in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper discusses the effectiveness of adversarial attacks and defenses, which falls under the computer security and cryptography (cs.CR) category. Finally, the paper uses high-resolution datasets, which is a common topic in multimedia (cs.MM).
